<info gid="714736670" type="Plot Summary">Yumi is a teacher at Seimei Academy. Raped by her ex-fiancé, she has little trust for men and rightfully so. During a teacher party, the vice principal slips her a drug to take advantage of her. Kidnapped, repeatedly raped, and filmed, she is turned into his sex toy. Katsutoshi, her student who helped in her kidnapping, is told that she was only going to be frightened a little as a prank and is horrified when she is raped and humiliated before his eyes. He wants to help her, he truly does, but he also has to think of Keiko, his childhood friend. If he betrays their secret to anyone, the vice principal and his henchman Gondo promise to take it out on her. Stuck between the decision to save his admired teacher and protect the woman that he loves, Katsutoshi's choice could either destroy them all or be their salvation.</info>
